text: My molar tooth filling fell out after chewing on some sticky nougat so i called the nearest dentist for sos. Receptionist was very kind and helpful. Dentist and his team was professional, friendly yet reassuring. Definitely recommend!

Dr Jeremy has provided me with exceptional service. He was able to provide me with professional advices specifically catered to my needs. I would definitely recommend anyone who is seeking for dental treatment with TDH. Nurse Xiao Wei is so caring and receptionist Norain and Pathin is so helpfully and caring. Thanks guys for your good services.
Best dental experience with Dr Jeremy who is attentive and meticulous. Most of all, he always puts his patients at ease. The staff is perpetually courteous and serves with a wide smile.

Have been taken care of by Dr Jeremy Ng for quite a few years already. He is pro and friendly.  He did my first tooth extraction and was painless! He knew is my first tooth extraction and was very patient and explained every single step he is going to do. Have recommended to a colleague but colleague found the price at Dental Hub a bit ex then neighbourhood clinic.

Maybe Dental hub can introduce some package say 2 times tooth scaling and polishing per year at a discounted price.
Have been seeing Dr Jeremy Ng for a few years now and I feel very comfortable under his care and i trust him with my dental needs. Staff at the Alexandra outlet are also friendly and warm.
